  <refsynopsisdiv id='synopsis'>
    <cmdsynopsis>
      <command>glassplayer</command>
      <arg choice='opt'><replaceable>OPTIONS</replaceable></arg>
      <arg choice='req'><replaceable>stream-url</replaceable></arg>
      <sbr/>
    </cmdsynopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>

  <refsect1 id='description'><title>Description</title>
  <para>
    <command>glassplayer</command><manvolnum>1</manvolnum> is an audio player
    that is capable of capturing and playing live streams from IceCast or
    ShoutCast streaming servers.
  </para>

  <para>
    <command>glassplayer</command><manvolnum>1</manvolnum> has no GUI or
    configuration file components at all; its sole 'user interface' is its
    command-line invocation.
  </para>
  </refsect1>

